 skewer inserted into the centre of the cake comes out clean. Leave cake to cool in tin, and then dust with icing sugar, slice and serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can serve this cake warm if desired. Try drizzling over a warm caramel sauce for an extra decadent treat."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 30m","12 portion"]}